message.raw:
* Make use of channel-specific amplitude unit conversion.
* Updates required following release of ARF/XRF firmware v1.5.7:
   - Make use of HEXENTRY table query command.
   - Declaring the number of table entries is fragile.
   - Use three dummy instructions instead of two at the start of the table.
